{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4c29c53ca8","title":"打丁德降胜利后立即打周祥初","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d3e9f3162f","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":21,"articleId":"4c29c53ca8"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"027d9abd02","type":"paragraph","text":"打丁德降胜利后立即打周祥初","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"aeb04a5919","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年11月21日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"132ac8baa3","type":"paragraph","text":"昨日止敌情大体明白，第一旅及孔令愉则在大水坑一带，周祥初在攀家沟、保宁堡一带，昨日一部向山城堡，主力二十一日当向山城堡以北距离三、四十里地区前进。丁德隆在山城堡一带。第二旅似在豫旺整理，胡军部到豫旺。我本日打丁师，除周师下午或能赶到外，余均须第三天方能赶到，到亦疲劳不堪。我打丁师胜利后，须立即整顿队势打周师","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"7e62196a91","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"c6b126a407","type":"paragraph","text":"二十一日三时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"70a15bec93","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军前敌总指挥部的电报。当时彭德怀任总指挥兼政治委员。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"47ba50d56b","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]孔令恂，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一路第二纵队第九十七师师长。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"a0814f42e2","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]周祥初，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一路第二纵队第四十三师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"abd6036e35","type":"paragraph","text":"14]丁德隆，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一路第二纵队第七十八师师长。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"21e6e692ee","type":"paragraph","text":"151豫旺，旧县名，县治在今宁夏同心县下马关。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"7a2b6bbe58","type":"paragraph","text":"[6]胡，指胡宗南，当时任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一路第二纵队司令兼第一师师长。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"33c9f17437","type":"paragraph","text":"室","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"},{"id":"569fb67f0c","type":"paragraph","text":"面对国民党军的“围”，毛泽东、彭德怀等指挥红军沉着应战，1936年11月取得山城堡战役的胜利。图为回师陕北后的彭德怀。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8"}],"page":{"id":"7c4cf99951","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"4c29c53ca8","start":10,"end":11}}}},"__N_SSG":true}